Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.51,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}明明 总是想要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.93,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}去往某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:06.17,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}却总是躲在你的身后
