Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.03,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}如果能稍微离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.99,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}这样 凝视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:35.43,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}就悄悄告诉你重要的话
