Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:04.09,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}很快 暴风雨就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:10.64,sogtra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}穿越原野
